		"description": "<p>Your conviction and the powerful alchemy surging through your veins combine to make you a uniquely implacable warrior. You can be slowed, but seldom stopped. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Your Strength, Constitution, Intelligence, or Charisma score increases by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li>\n<li>Half your bloodblade levels count as herald levels for the purpose of the @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.2td6srku3ln8qasl]{Inspiring Devotion} feature.</li>\n<li>Half your herald levels count as bloodblade levels for the purpose of the Unnatural Mien feature.</li>\n<li>If you would suffer the charmed, confused, or frightened condition, you can spend a hit die as a reaction to suffer a level of strife instead.</li>\n<li>If you would suffer the blinded, deafened, poisoned, or stunned condition, you can spend a hit die as a reaction to suffer a level of fatigue instead.</li>\n</ul>",
